data.description: Selling at auction! November 29, 2023! PLEASE NOTE: $20,000 is only the auction start price and has not bearing on the actual market value.  Discover this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom house set on a spacious 1.75-acre lot. The kitchen offers potential for customization, while the open living area is perfect for gatherings. The rustic landscape presents an opportunity for creative landscaping, with room to create your own tranquil haven. The peaceful neighborhood provides easy access to amenities, schools, and parks. With a little imagination, this property has the potential to become a beautiful retreat that blends the comforts of home with the beauty of nature. Contact us today to explore this unique opportunity.
